nodes.text: The Gwendolyn 6 was an expensive make of processor chip used in IT-3 Interrogator droids and developed between 6 ABY and 8 ABY by the company MerenData. It included tachyon processing bands, quantum RAM, and biocell storage and gave the IT-3 an edge over the ISB-120 as its processing speed was 50.32 times greater than the ISB.
